snippet.title: Agent 9 (Prime 8) [CANCELLED! - PS2 Target Render / Concept Trailer]
snippet.description: http://www.unseen64.net - A cancelled platform / action game based on Agent 9, the monkey from the Spyro The Dragon series. This is just an early target render, later the game was redesigned with a new style, but neither version ever came out.
